default function ProfileDetailsPage() { const navigate = useNavigate(); const { user } = useAuth(); const [error, setError] = useState(""); const [formData, setFormData] = useState({ orgName: "", location: "", homepage: "", coreValues: "", fieldOfInterest: "", partnershipGoal: "", resourcesProvided: "", // 添加任何后端需要的其他字段 }); const [selectedState, setSelectedState] = useState(""); const [availableCities, setAvailableCities] = useState([]); useEffect(() => { const orgType = localStorage.getItem("orgType"); if (!orgType) { navigate("/profile-setup/type"); } }, [navigate]); useEffect(() => { if (selectedState && CITIES_BY_STATE[selectedState]) { setAvailableCities(CITIES_BY_STATE[selectedState]); } else { setAvailableCities([]); } setFormData((prev) => ({ ...prev, location: selectedState ? `${selectedState} - ` : "", })); }, [selectedState]); const handleSubmit = async (e) => { e.preventDefault(); setError(""); console.log("开始提交表单数据..."); try { // 检查并打印要发送的数据 const profileData = { ...formData, orgType: localStorage.getItem("orgType"), coreValues: formData.coreValues.split(",").map((v) => v.trim()), }; console.log("准备发送的数据:", profileData); const response = await fetch("http://localhost:3001/api/profile", { method: "POST", headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json", Authorization: `Bearer ${localStorage.getItem("token")}`, }, body: JSON.stringify(profileData), }); const text = await response.text(); console.log("服务器原始响应:", text); try { const data = JSON.parse(text); console.log("解析后的响应:", data); if (response.ok) { console.log("个人资料保存成功"); // 更新 AuthContext 中的用户信息 if (user) { user.orgName = formData.orgName; } // 跳转到主页 navigate("/"); } else { console.error("保存失败:", data); setError(data.message || "Failed to save profile. Please try again."); } } catch (parseError) { console.error("解析响应失败:", parseError); setError("Server response format error. Please try again."); } } catch (networkError) { console.error("网络错误:", networkError); setError("Network error. Please check your connection."); } }; const handleChange = (e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; if (name === "state") { setSelectedState(value); } else if (name === "city") { setFormData((prev) => ({ ...prev, location: `${selectedState} - ${value}`, })); } else { setFormData((prev) => ({ ...prev, [name]: value, })); } }; return (

{error}
